<parameternamelist>
<parametername>uint16_t</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>freq Is the frequency to change. For example, FM =&gt; 10390 = 103.9 MHz; AM =&gt; 810 = 810 KHz. </para>
